<p class="">In the same way, the policy of the Kremlin—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9ef65b0a-3aaa-4334-a1e4-5cb56cbb2237" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
