<p class="">Further to that point of Order. There is no fact whatever concerning the existence of the Czar or Czarism in Russia. This is a deliberate attempt to make a case. The Czar was the right hon. Gentleman's own old friend.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
