<p class="">In point of fact, is that not hurting the Germans rather than the Russians?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e8160b21-9447-439b-b026-e16cfed202d6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
