            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a0b42a4f-7c20-45b2-a763-bc3c265d66e6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
