                Mr. Platts-Mills
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f1860b87-2b5d-4cea-b1d7-b2ef7751b1be" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
