<p class="">Had it no effect in withdrawing our ambassador from Spain?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5fd2daa2-8118-4dac-ba8f-b285d9700a62" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
