<p class="">Is the hon. Member's proposal that we should send conscripts from this country to take part in the war in Greece?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f1586150-7ea0-4e87-a905-e468de0b55aa" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
