            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-82329e4e-41c5-4402-9d80-42d38464694e">
                Mr. Gallacher
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-82329e4e-41c5-4402-9d80-42d38464694e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
